    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚与越南在中美竞争中升级外交关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/australia-vietnam-upgrade-diplomatic-ties-amid-us-china-rivalry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国地区影响力不断上升的背景下，堪培拉采取行动加强整个亚太地区的联系，澳大利亚与美国一起将与越南的外交关系提升到最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-07/australia-vietnam-upgrade-diplomatic-ties-amid-us-china-rivalry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 00:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
